{"tid":470310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［異形］南韓醫生：脫北士兵體內藏大量寄生蟲，手術時四處竄動","createTime":"2017-11-16T07:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T13:33:22.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"50f8dbd7daf35349e42846f3ba94068feca16377","tid":470310,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:38:07.000Z","msg":"北韓一名士兵本周一在兩韓非軍事區（DMZ）投誠，由於他身中多槍，南韓醫師為他進行多次手術搶救，意外在他體內發現大量寄生蟲，其中最大的長達27公分，在手術期間不斷鑽出來。醫師說，從醫20多年，從未在臨床治療上看過這些種類的寄生蟲。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n《朝鮮日報》報導，負責手術的李國宗醫師昨日在記者會上表示：「從進行第一次手術時起，腹腔內部被糞便、寄生蟲污染的狀況就非常嚴重，今後還可能出現併發症。」李國宗說，在該士兵破裂的小腸內部，發現了幾十條最大長度為27釐米的寄生蟲。而且在手術過程中，寄生蟲不斷從受損的內臟鑽出來，和糞便混在一起造成污染，讓醫生很是頭痛。<br />\n<br />\n李醫生說：「我們發現了不可能在南韓人身上發現的寄生蟲」，「作為外科醫生，我20年都沒見過這種寄生蟲，只是在教科書上見到過。」<br />\n<br />\n推測這名年齡為20多歲的士兵，身高170公分左右，體重約為60公斤，體型比南韓成年男性要矮小和清瘦。小腸長度為160公分，短于南韓男性的平均值200公分。李國宗說：「應該是由於小腸短，導致消化功能不完善」，「在小腸中發現的食物凝固成類似糞便的狀態，應該是存在攝食問題，實際上他的營養狀態也不佳。」在該士兵的腹腔內發現了糞便和少量食物，但大部分是玉米粒。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171116/1242248/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171116%2F1242248%2F&d=sQ4oYIzeAoHlPV%2Fmw8DhpRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=78996c57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171116%2F1242248%2F&h=4f207a48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171116/1242248/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/153718_219437a07e36e37e0975d4596cd9d208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F153718_219437a07e36e37e0975d4596cd9d208.jpg&h=d2f1805f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/153719_5bab4743f9ff4d6f8fa1344d16b214cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F153719_5bab4743f9ff4d6f8fa1344d16b214cf.jpg&h=bb051ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪盎毒來架，打鼓就痛"},{"pid":"63ea1488e23027c515456247bae2ca28994fc619","tid":470310,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"170⋯⋯香港大部分男人ge高度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf970d67dfde8138413d3529e29ee74dfc71053","tid":470310,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:42:09.000Z","msg":"生化武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875b5c3f062166dc9c2e8e375b62c18c8218d31d","tid":470310,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"南韓男人平均身高有撚 170"},{"pid":"3d1bf6ec1347f4743bb00de71353439cfaaf2d6d","tid":470310,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>170⋯⋯香港大部分男人ge高度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你就你啦"},{"pid":"5a8ce15987ed18948c7bb072bf43dc57bca5049d","tid":470310,"uid":324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T13:33:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南韓男人平均身高有撚 170</blockquote><br />\n唔係講條腸咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}